This is just a little AppleScript project I used to learn how to use the language. It uses AppleScript's native ability to take iTunes info and print it.

The song time, song title, album title, and artist are listed. This works best with GeekTool () with a refresh rate of 1 second to provide a constant update on your desktop. This is a very lightweight program and with GeekTool, it is just rolled into the GeekTool process and is windowless.
